  "title": "A man spotted a large round UFO with 2 dots on its top in Porto Alegre-RS [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-man-spotted-a-large-round-ufo-with-2-dots-on-its-top-in-porto-alegre-rs-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1eR",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 20th, 1996</strong>. Time: 19h35. Duration: 10 minutes. A person in Porto Alegre, State of Rio Grande do Sul, observed a large round UFO with two dots on its top, moving 15 away from him. According to the witness, the unidentified flying object was gray, but sometimes red and green. The UFO was described as &#8220;slower than an aircraft&#8221;, and left a &#8220;tail of light&#8221; when moving in its straight path. The witness claimed to have taken photographs of the sighting, but these photos were not made available. The event was seen under good visibility and clear skies.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.413. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Porto Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
